spring - Spring Boot CLI

USAGE:
    spring [init] [spring-cli-args...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Spring Boot CLI wrapper for Spring project management.
    Automatically initializes git repository and commits changes.

ARGUMENTS:
    init
        Initialize new Spring project with extraction

    spring-cli-args
        Arguments passed to Spring Boot CLI

EXAMPLES:
    spring init
    spring init --package=com.example --dependencies=web,data-jpa
    spring run app.groovy
